data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home on over 1/2 an acre of land with endless privacy on a quiet cul-de-sac surrounded by farms. No HOA or county taxes! Open floor plan w/new flooring throughout. Modern kitchen & an oversized island are open to dining & living areas w/built-in shelving that creates a cozy atmosphere perfect for relaxing after a long day. Spacious primary ensuite w/crown molding & double sinks. 2 spacious & comfy secondary bedrooms & full bathroom in the hallway. You will appreciate the large laundry room & mudroom w/private side-door entrance. Imagine enjoying the above ground pool and beautiful views from the back deck, surrounded by peace & quiet. Located in the country, yet conveniently close to highways, schools & shopping centers. Off-frame modular, appraised the same as a site or stick-built home & has a permanent foundation, making it eligible for all financing options. Rare opportunity to own a property that offers both privacy & convenience. Come & see!
